<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">

</head>
<body background = "gambar 1.jpg">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm">

            </div>
            <div class="col-sm">
                <br/><br/>
                <form class="form-signin" action="/inputpembayaran" method="GET">
                    <div class="text-center mb-4">
                        <img class="mb-4" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ozqXWADdJPs/UW7TySb6iJI/AAAAAAAAAKo/_NmAZsiRoVk/s1600/logo+smk.jpg"
                            alt="" width="72" height="72">
                        <h1 class="h3 mb-3 font-weight-normal">Login account</h1>
                        <p>Kami menyediakan berbagai fitur menarik untuk kamu jelajahi. sing-in untu mengetahui lebih lanjut</p>
                        <p><code>: 12340000</code> pseudo-element.<a href="https://caniuse.com/#feat=css-placeholder-shown">Works in latest</a>             
                        <a href="https://caniuse.com/#feat=css-placeholder-shown"> Chrome, Safari, Firefox, and IE
                                10/11
                                (prefixed).</a></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-label-group">
                        <input type="email" id="inputEmail" class="form-control" placeholder="Email address" required
                            autofocus>
                        <label for="inputEmail"></label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-label-group">
                        <input type="password" id="inputPassword" class="form-control" placeholder="Password" required>
                        <label for="inputPassword"></label>
                    </div>
                    <input type="checkbox"> Remember Me
                    <a href="/inputpembayaran"><button class="btn btn-lg btn-primary btn-block" type="submit">Sign in</button></a>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm">

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
        
</body>
</html>
